---
import Section from './ui/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="use-cases">
  <div class="header">
    <h2 class="heading">You've been here before.</h2>
    <p class="subheading">The frustration is real. So is the fix.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cases">
    <div class="case">
      <div class="case-label">"I know I wrote this down somewhere"</div>
      <p class="case-body">
        You remember the idea. You don't remember when, where, or what you called it. Type a
        fragment — a feeling, a phrase, half a concept. SoNoted finds it. Every time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="case">
      <div class="case-label">Everything you know, before you walk in</div>
      <p class="case-body">
        Board call in 20 minutes. SoNoted surfaces every note you've taken on that company — the
        concerns they raised six months ago, the numbers you jotted after the last meeting, the
        follow-up you never sent. You walk in prepared. Always.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="case">
      <div class="case-label">Two years of thinking, on demand</div>
      <p class="case-body">
        You've been collecting notes on a topic for years across three different apps. Ask SoNoted a
        question. It synthesizes an answer from your own thinking — not the internet's. The
        connection you made at 2am in 2022 shows up exactly when you need it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .heading {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }
  }

  .subheading {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cases {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cases {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .case {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    transition:
      border-color 200ms ease,
      box-shadow 200ms ease;
  }

  .case:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--color-accent-glow);
  }

  .case-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .case-body {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
